  "commit_message": "perf: replace fmt.Sprintf with strconv in ExplainSQL numeric formatting (#7796)\n\nReplace fmt.Sprintf(\"%d\") and fmt.Sprintf(\"%.6f\") with strconv.FormatInt,\nstrconv.FormatUint, and strconv.FormatFloat in logger/sql.go ExplainSQL.\n\nThese calls are hit every time a SQL query is logged. Using strconv avoids\nthe format string parsing overhead of fmt.Sprintf.\n\nAlso split the combined int/uint case in the fmt.Stringer branch into\nseparate cases to use the correct strconv function for each kind.\n\nBenchma",
